data.description:
Welcome Home! Looking for that perfect condo with plenty of character that is move in ready!? 
This cozy and spacious 3 bedroom 2 full bathroom condo is located within the Historic Hoskins Mill Community. Boasting 18' ceilings with exposed wood, unique brick walls, with 12 feet tall oversized windows, perfect for allowing plenty of natural sunlight. Enjoy the convenience of 2 bedrooms and a full bathroom on the main level. The flex space on the main level is perfect for entertaining, or utilizing as a home office. Upstairs you'll find a spacious loft/bedroom with an ensuite bathroom and walk in closet. One of the few units in the building with built in washer and dryer connections. The building includes an elevator and plenty of parking within a gated community. Showings to begin Thursday, 6/29.
